text: Borisovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Bakeyevsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 35 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 15 km from Sterlibashevo, 3 km from Bakeyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Borisovka, Sterlibashevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
